  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-001">.NET 8 Minimal API + BackgroundService. No Azure Functions for gate resolution. Async-friendly contract.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-008">Endpoint-filter authorization. Gate resolution endpoints (added by resolvers in 031–034) MUST use `.AddEndpointFilter&lt;&gt;()`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">Feature-module DI: `AddActionEngineModule()`. ≤15 non-framework registrations across all of ActionEngine.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">AI Architecture (refined 2026-05-20). BFF placement; CRUD-side consumers reach `IGateResolver` via `PublicContracts/` facade only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Audit per gate decision: Tier 2 hash + Tier 3 work history. Contract defines audit fields (`ActionRunId`, `ToolDispatchId`, `GateType`, `GateDecision`, `RequestedByUserId`, `ResolvedByUserId?`, `ResolvedAtUtc`, `Reason?`).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-019">ProblemDetails (RFC 7807) for any HTTP surface added by resolvers.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Publish-size delta ≤ 5 MB compressed (NFR-10). This task adds ≤200 LoC of interface + DTOs; expected delta &lt; 0.1 MB.</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md">Pre-merge checklist: placement decision = BFF (no facade leakage); no new NuGet packages; ADRs cited; publish-size impact verified.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">5-min default timeout uniform across resolvers; configurable per-Action via `GateRequest.TimeoutSeconds`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">`GateType.Custom` deferred to R2 — 5 enum values only in MVP.</constraint>
  </constraints>

